isn't it? It's not broken.

68
00:04:16,668 --> 00:04:19,337
Well I heard sometimes a sprain
can be worse than a break.

69
00:04:19,338 --> 00:04:22,247
Oh, is that one worse?!
- Yes, it is! Much worse!

70
00:04:22,248 --> 00:04:23,999
Well, I said
I was sorry!

71
00:04:24,635 --> 00:04:25,618
Can I fix you
something to eat?

72
