76
00:04:36,643 --> 00:04:38,182
Dick, you sound pretty pathetic.

77
00:04:38,183 --> 00:04:40,079
Is it pathetic
to sprain your foot,

78
00:04:40,080 --> 00:04:43,251
worse than anybody ever in the
history of the world. Sally!

79
00:04:44,118 --> 00:04:46,022
Sorry, Dick. But you know
nothing about earth pain

