for selling this crap?

100
00:05:43,826 --> 00:05:46,017
You get the satisfaction
of helping to pay to

101
00:05:46,018 --> 00:05:47,182
send the band
to Washington!

102
00:05:47,183 --> 00:05:50,815
Now how's that for compensation?!
- Oh, all right, cool.

103
00:05:52,384 --> 00:05:53,614
That's that.

104
00:05:53,872 --> 00:05:55,480
I'm Gonna practise some ball passing.

105
00:05:55,981 --> 00:05:56,877
I want half of you
over there,

106
00:05:56,878 --> 00:05:57,765
half of you over there,

107
00:05:57,766 --> 00:05:58,977
the other half
come with me.

108
00:06:10,216 --> 00:06:11,928
I brought you some soup.

109
00:06:13,552 --> 00:06:16,019
Let me just fix
this foot here.

110
00:06:20,358 --> 00:06:22,389
Eat your soup.
- Okay.

111
00:06:25,638 --> 00:06:27,890
Mmm, this tastes
sumptuous.

112
00:06:27,891 --> 00:06:30,046
My mother used to make this soup
for me whenever I ..

113
