just to make sure
it heals properly?

194
00:11:34,924 --> 00:11:35,560
No.

195
00:11:36,075 --> 00:11:37,273
Doctor, you don't understand.

196
00:11:37,700 --> 00:11:39,172
The moment I sprained
that foot,

197
00:11:39,173 --> 00:11:42,052
