of my treatment options!

202
00:11:54,225 --> 00:11:58,497
Because it's not the length of our time here
that matters, it's the quality of our lives!

203
00:11:58,598 --> 00:12:00,449
And if you're not qualified
to break my foot,

204
00:12:00,450 --> 00:12:03,429
then by god, I'll find
a doctor who will!

205
