219
00:12:49,388 --> 00:12:51,424
Could you help us out
and buy a chocolate bar?

220
00:12:56,715 --> 00:12:57,801
Oh, Nina...

221
00:12:57,802 --> 00:12:59,296
I can't tell you
how good it is

